You are an AI coding assistant for the Meli-Portfolio-Resume project — Victor's portfolio to apply for dev roles at Mercado Livre.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 16 (Turbopack), React 18, Tailwind CSS v4 + custom CSS
- Framer Motion, Recharts 3.x, react-icons, @lottiefiles/dotlottie-react
- MongoDB Atlas, Vercel Blob for image storage
- Custom i18n (EN/ES/PT), Zustand, Zod, TanStack Query, axios
- Lint-free, type-checked build via `npm run build`

## Project Structure
- `src/app/` — Next.js App Router pages: layout, home, gallery, galleryAdmin (auth), meli-it-case (job form)
- `src/app/api/` — gallery (CRUD, auth), applications (job submission)
- `src/components/` — Hero, About, TechSection, Skills, Projects, Contact, MeliHeroSection, MeliFeaturesSection, GalleryLightbox, etc.
- `src/lib/` — i18n, mongodb, auth (Bearer token), validate (CPF/CEP/email), rateLimit (20/min)
- `src/style/` — styles.css (all CSS), DotPattern.jsx, BackToTop.jsx, animations.js

## Conventions
- Use Framer Motion variants from `src/style/animations.js` for animations
- Use `t(key, lang)` from `src/lib/i18n.js` for translations (en/es/pt)
- Use `useTheme()` hook for dark/light mode
- Use `useGalleryImages`, `useUploadImage`, `useDeleteImage`, `useUpdateSettings`, `useSubmitContact` from TanStack Query hooks
- Icons: react-icons (Io5, Fa, Tb, Si) — no new icon libraries
- CSS variables: --accent, --bg-app, --bg-hero, --text-main from styles.css
- Keep the MELI brand aesthetic (yellow #FFE600 accent in dark, deep blue #2D3277 in light)

## OpenCode Agents
- `fast` agent → DeepSeek V4 Flash Free (code, commands, fixes). Invoke with `@fast`
- `plan` agent → DeepSeek R1 (architecture, code review). Tab-switch to Plan mode
- `gemini` agent → Gemini 2.5 Flash (multimodal: images, audio, docs). Invoke with `@gemini`

## Auth & Security
- Admin: Bearer token via `ADMIN_API_KEY` env var, Zustand store with persist
- Rate limit: 20 req/min per IP (in-memory Map in `src/lib/rateLimit.js`)
- Images: client-side Canvas compression (2000px, JPEG q0.85) → Vercel Blob or Sharp WebP fallback to MongoDB base64
- Job form: CPF/phone/CEP auto-format + validation, age check, PCD conditional field

## Env (.env.local — gitignored)
- MONGODB_URI, ADMIN_API_KEY, BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN
